_name": "Screenshot-Ice.png", "id": "1018062432708421", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031529_1018062436041754_1577944608711742886_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=mxkL5VUWXacQ7kNvgFIh3bI&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCPIJYCML2qaQ9YM5H6pyQdu6hHaigMfUr7xaMpAw2cSw&oe=67137E8E"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "HITSTREAM_Cover_FINAL_PASSOFF.png", "id": "876481967757738", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982539_876481977757737_2671632885756691458_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=sF1481_WeL8Q7kNvgGoL0dl&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDnOauLNjkayh2DYd-4IJXeS4hAtSC0e0tIUkxnJu-ucg&oe=6713980F"}, "display_name": "Hitstream", "keywords": ["fitness", "movement", "rhythm", "music", "wellbeing"], "long_description": "Fitness made fun!\n\nThe challenge surrounds you in this 360\u2019 game that takes you on a cardio-boosting trip around the world. So good you won\u2019t even realise you\u2019re exercising!\n\n\ud83c\udfae Over 12 hours of gameplay\n\n\ud83e\udd4a Punch, stretch, squat & dodge moves\n\n\ud83d\udd25 Lite, standard & intense modes\n\n\ud83c\udfdd\ufe0f Stunning scenery \n\n\ud83d\udcaa Full-body movement\n\n\ud83c\udfb5 Awesome tunes\n\n\ud83d\udd7a Intuitive choreography\n\n\ud83d\udc6bMultiplayer\n\n\ud83e\ude9fMixed reality\n\nDesigned with positive energy and physical/mental wellbeing in mind, this immersive game will take you on a range of journeys, from uplifting adventures that work on agility to power-focused routines that build strength and stamina. \n\nThe perfect non-subscription addition to your VR fitness library. \n\nHitstream: where will you exercise today?", "short_description": "Fitness made fun! \nThe challenge surrounds you in this 360\u2019 game that takes you on a cardio-boosting trip around the world. So good you won\u2019t even realise you\u2019re exercising!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "dev